{"id": "1201845669690888262", "channel_id": "1201845669690888262", "type": 0, "author_id": "699270788578148442", "author_name": "_buqi", "author_bot": false, "content": "設在圖1的位置紅圈或其他位置\n\n目前要進到冶煉室 \n要先點物資再點分解\n或是\n點材料再跳轉", "timestamp": "2024-01-30T11:05:36.867000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1201845669867036732", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-01-30-19-00-19-30_6120889c12ac7e9ba4b3ef1f073858ff.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 105530, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1201845669690888262/1201845669867036732/Screenshot_2024-01-30-19-00-19-30_6120889c12ac7e9ba4b3ef1f073858ff.jpg?ex=6a006680&is=69ff1500&hm=f64050c38feb5aab62955dfbc6eb3ecb56a3cc377640dd7f77dffd08e3bbefe5&"}, {"id": "1201845670131282020", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-01-30-19-00-45-83_6120889c12ac7e9ba4b3ef1f073858ff.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1735, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1201845669690888262/1201845670131282020/Screenshot_2024-01-30-19-00-45-83_6120889c12ac7e9ba4b3ef1f073858ff.jpg?ex=6a006680&is=69ff1500&hm=91583d35a42b74f6f3ed25f519dad6123dc54fafc2d2012fa3032798e1d46efb&"}, {"id": "1201845670412034048", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-01-30-19-01-29-10_6120889c12ac7e9ba4b3ef1f073858ff.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 4623, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1201845669690888262/1201845670412034048/Screenshot_2024-01-30-19-01-29-10_6120889c12ac7e9ba4b3ef1f073858ff.jpg?ex=6a006681&is=69ff1501&hm=eaecc5e533edcfa872e94f59d2376f0969ef2a9e61f2d05657f2e78b0cc1405d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1201845669690888262", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」能不能設個冶煉室的入口", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1201715754915856474", "channel_id": "1201715754915856474", "type": 0, "author_id": "371624648078524416", "author_name": "devis0212", "author_bot": false, "content": "校貓對於放毒有什麼樣的期許，珈倫莉莉都給了對於萬血boss少之又少的施毒量。\n先不提寧妃以及莉茲的差距了，對於毒這種需要時間回合數才能打出傷害的機制。\n給莉莉30-50的毒量給珈倫30的毒量這對於後期根本於事無補而且讓人搞不懂角色的定位以及技能的用處。\n\n輔助能力給個建議是 打個比方\n莉莉覺醒施放護盾給最高血量的35毒\n能改成 給5%當前毒量(最低35毒)\n\n講回去莉茲寧妃的差距 \n能理解莉茲道中不舒服王關暢快的想法 但寧妃我試了很多方法不管是疊力量爆發輸出疊毒又或者每回合開狂氣拉高輸出次數\n都沒辦法在後期連普通小怪都萬血的情況下稍微輕鬆獲勝 反倒是莉茲道中過得比寧妃舒服\n\n對於這兩個角色設計組能不能做點權衡利弊\n大概就這樣", "timestamp": "2024-01-30T02:29:22.771000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-30T02:32:17.442000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1201715754915856474", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "放毒的標準", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1201885565562404906", "channel_id": "1201885565562404906", "type": 0, "author_id": "830435120590487562", "author_name": "0620n", "author_bot": false, "content": "請問時間原點不能回溯限定池角色和命輪嗎？\n像是紅夫人或者圖魯\n命途回溯之芯能否放到下個月或者幾個月後選當期限定命輪？\n靈魂回溯之心能否放到下個月或者幾個月後選當期限定角色？", "timestamp": "2024-01-30T13:44:08.784000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-30T13:47:11.480000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1201885565562404906", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」時間原點", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
